txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Spotted ears from the beasts in western Dunland. Collect them and deliver them to the taskmaster in Galtrev to earn favour with the Men of Dunland.
'The local beasts often stalk our herds. You have kept them at bay, and we will see what we can do in return.'
'These creatures harry our livestock relentlessly...you will not have to go far to find them.'
Men of Dunland Task: Spotted Ears
The Dunlending taskmaster wants spotted ears. She can be found at Galtrev in Pren Gwydh.
Deliver the spotted ears to the taskmaster in Galtrev.
You have accepted a task to acquire spotted ears. You are to deliver them to the Dunlending taskmaster in Galtrev.
Wanted: Spotted ears from the beasts in western Dunland.
